{
  "stem": "182.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As children at that time I had a feeling we can travel lighter because it was heavy to schlep the things that we had on our backs.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, they took everything away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we arrived again to a Jewish family on the border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were very, very, very nice and very understanding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They gave us room to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all they could feed us was with oat gruel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now I don't know if you know how oat gruel tastes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- the-- the flake of the oat-- the oat that we eat is already-- the outside is taken off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And what is around it is very sharp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It has a point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And to eat that, it's terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But that's what they had to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Anyway, it came night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Everybody got a walking stick, and we started to cross the border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we crossed the border back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And as soon as we came down from the mountain and we were going-- like here was the river, here were the houses and we were going behind them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the guard duty was going on the road here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they noticed us, and they-- they-- they're taking us back to the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They're going to take us back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now my father gave himself-- my father gave himself an insulin shot, which if you get an insulin shot, your nose starts running and your eyes water and you become disoriented, and it looks very bad.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when they took us to the-- to the top of the hill.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then my mother says to the Hungarian lieutenant or whatever his title was, that, look my husband is sick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He has to have a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
